for%20retirement%2C%26quot%3B%20Shelton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f2881905-8e95-4ba0-b030-b562fe6c64da%5C%22%3EThe%20retirement%20student%20debt%20crisis%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Shelton%20and%20Larry%20are%20facing%20a%20particular%20aspect%20of%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eretirement%20crisis%3A%20hoping%20to%20throw%20in%20the%20towel%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-social-security-gen-x-retirement-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esitting%20on%20mountains%20of%20student%20loan%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Over%20a%20million%20American%20ages%2055%20to%2064%20are%20either%20holding%20student%20loans%20or%20have%20spouses%20holding%20loans%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economicpolicyresearch.org%2Fresource-library%2Fhow-student-loan-debt-impedes-retirement-and-financial-security-for-older-workers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20School's%20Schwartz%20Center%20for%20Economic%20Policy%20Analysis%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Those%20loan%20holders%20said%20that%2C%20on%20average%2C%20they%20expect%20to%20take%2011%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eyears%20to%20repay%20their%20debts%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20can%20oftentimes%20end%20up%20being%20much%20longer%20due%20to%20interest%20and%20financial%20hardship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20Americans%20holding%20student%20loan%20debt%2C%20Gen%20Xers%20and%20boomers%20have%20the%20highest%20median%20balance%2C%20although%20only%20a%20small%20percentage%20of%20those%2055-64%20%E2%80%94%20around%2013%25%20%E2%80%94%20and%20those%2065-74%20%E2%80%94%20around%205%25%20%E2%80%94%20hold%20educational%20installment%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F5Tiit%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Educational%20installment%20loans%20by%20age%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22459%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20the%20other%20day%2C%20Shelton%20was%20checking%20what%20her%20Social%20Security%20check%20would%20look%20like%20at%20different%20retirement%20ages%2C%20since%20the%20program%20incentivizes%20waiting%20to%20collect%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20work%20until%20I'm%2070%2C%20that's%20where%20I've%20got%20the%20most%20amount.%20But%20that's%20still%20going%20to%20be%20tight%20when%20a%20quarter%20of%20that%20is%20a%20student%20loan%20payment%2C%26quot%3B%20Shelton%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20stresses%20me%20to%20no%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbidens-plan-to-prevent-spiraling-interest-on-student-loan-debt-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInterest%20is%20a%20key%20reason%3C%2Fa%3E%20many%20older%20adults%20find%20themselves%20struggling%20to%20pay%20off%20their%20student%20loans%20for%20decades.%20Since%20Larry%20could%20not%20afford%20to%20make%20payments%20for%20a%20period%20of%20time%20due%20to%20financial%20hardship%2C%20the%206.25%25%20interest%20rate%20caused%20his%20balance%20to%20grow%20larger%20than%20what%20he%20originally%20borrowed.%20It's%20an%20issue%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-single-mom-student-debt-plus-loans-set-to-double-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20PLUS%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-cheaper-payments-save-parent-plus-loans-relief-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20while%20they%20took%20out%20loans%20to%20give%20their%20children%20the%20best%20shot%20at%20a%20successful%20future%2C%20they%20didn't%20know%20at%20the%20time%20that%20doing%20so%20would%20leave%20them%20with%20balances%20they%20could%20not%20afford%20to%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E