.%20Despite%20the%20NTA's%20attempts%20to%20manage%20the%20fallout%2C%20accusations%20of%20a%20widespread%20leak%20persisted%2C%20prompting%20protests%20and%20legal%20actions%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20intervened%2C%20chastising%20the%20NTA%20for%20its%20handling%20of%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECentral%20to%20the%20unfolding%20scandal%20is%20Ravi%20Atri%2C%20known%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20previous%20exam%20paper%20leaks%20across%20various%20states.%20His%20modus%20operandi%20allegedly%20involved%20uploading%20solved%20question%20papers%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20through%20a%20network%20known%20as%20the%20'solver%20gang'.%20Atri's%20notoriety%20stretches%20back%20to%20his%20arrest%20in%202012%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20Crime%20Branch%20for%20his%20alleged%20role%20in%20leaking%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20Police%2C%20which%20initially%20arrested%20several%20individuals%20connected%20to%20the%20leak%2C%20including%20a%20student%20and%20accomplices%2C%20expanded%20its%20investigation%20beyond%20state%20borders.%20Connections%20to%20Atri%20surfaced%20during%20interrogations%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20eventual%20capture%20by%20the%20UP%20STF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202007%2C%20Atri's%20family%20sent%20him%20to%20Kota%20to%20prepare%20for%20his%20medical%20entrance%20exam.%20He%20cleared%20the%20exam%20in%202012%20and%20got%20admission%20in%20PGI%20Rohtak%2C%20but%20did%20not%20appear%20for%20the%20exam%20in%20the%20fourth%20year.%20Authorities%20said%20that%20by%20then%20he%20had%20come%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20'exam%20mafia'%20and%20was%20sitting%20as%20a%20proxy%20for%20other%20candidates.%20He%20also%20started%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20circulating%20the%20leaked%20papers%20among%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719050880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8kv66lcs_neet-exam-protest_625x300_22_June_