s%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterest-rate-hikes-cuts-fed-policy-outlook-kashkari-inflation-target-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterest%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20end%20of%20pandemic-era%20trends%20and%20a%20slowing%20economy%20overall%20has%20crimped%20demand%20for%20tech%20workers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20being%20said%2C%20employment%20in%20the%20tech%20sector%20has%20fallen%20less%20than%202%25%20since%20its%20peak%20in%20December%202022%20and%20is%20still%2021%25%20higher%20than%20March%202020%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENela%20Richardson%2C%20ADP's%20chief%20economist%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20software%20developer%20isn't%20%26quot%3Ban%20out-of-date%20occupation%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20could%20take%20longer%20to%20land%20work%20given%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bbecome%20a%20very%20efficient%20occupation%26quot%3B%20where%20fewer%20workers%20are%20likely%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20may%20not%2C%20as%20a%20young%20tech%20worker%20in%20this%20industry%2C%20get%20recruited%20straight%20away%20out%20of%20university%20or%20learn%20straight%20away%20from%20your%20first%20job%2C%20or%20that%20there%20may%20have%20to%20be%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20grinding%2C%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20of%20a%20normal%20labor%20market%20in%20terms%20of%20new%20hires%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FDbSRx%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22US%20software%20developer%20employment%20index%20%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22495%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20in%20software%20developer%20employment%20could%20partly%20be%20attributed%20to%20changes%20in%20consumer%20spending%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20slowdown%20in%20software%20developer%20hires%20in%202020%2C%20and%20then%20we%20had%20a%20couple%20bounce%20backs%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that's%20reflective%20of%20how%20the%20pandemic%20really%20spurred%20this%20increase%20into%20digital%20service%20offerings%2C%26quot%3B%20Richardson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJob-search%20platform%20Indeed%20has%20its%20own%20running%20index%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ejob%20postings%20for%20the%20software%20development%20sector.%20Nick%20Bunker%2C%20economic%20research%20director%20for%20North%20America%20at%20the%20Indeed%20Hiring%20Lab%2C%20told%20BI%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20unlikely%20we'll%20see%20levels%20of%20demand%20like%20we%20saw%20in%20'21%2C%20in%20'22%20for%20software%20development%20anytime%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Bunker%20said%20demand%20for%20these%20jobs%20is%20healthy%2C%20and%20these%20are%20still%20well-paying%20gigs.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bls.gov%2Foes%2Fcurrent%2Foes151252.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBureau%20of%20Labor%20Statistics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20median%20annual%20wage%20for%20software%20developers%20was%20%24132%2C270.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FCygK0%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22How%20job%20opportunities%20look%20in%20the%20US%20software%20development%20sector%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22483%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20depressed%20state%20of%20postings%20for%20software%20development%20jobs%20could%20be%20a%20possibly%20cyclical%20story%20or%20short-term%20story%2C%26quot%3B%20Bunker%20said.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20this%20is%20just%20interest%20rates%20are%20still%20very%20high%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20employers%20are%20looking%20to%20be%20very%20cautious%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20hiring%20because%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20firms%20overhired%20in%20'21%2C%20and%20maybe%20they're%20just%20being%20very%20patient%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22077ceaa5-2089-4556-9f27-290c963e7db0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%20for%20experienced%20workers%20seeking%20a%20better-paying%20gig%20and%20for%20new%20graduates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EZhao%20also%20noted%20%26quot%3Bweak%26quot%3B%20sentiment%20in%20the%20tech%20sector%20and%20noted%20this%20could%20be%20because%20%26quot%3Bwaves%20of%20new%20graduates%20have%20been%20racing%20to%20enter%20the%20tech%20industry%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20as%20tech%20employers%20have%20offered%20high%20pay%20for%20newly%20minted%20software%20developers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhao%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Beven%20for%20experienced%20software%20developers%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20market%2C%20the%20issue%20may%20not%20be%20difficulty%20finding%20a%20job%20at%20all%2C%20but%20rather%20difficulty%20finding%20a%20job%20that%20pays%20as%20well%20as%20their%20previous%20one.%20Swallowing%20a%20pay%20cut%20is%20a%20tough%20ask%20for%20software%20developers%20who%20were%20earning%20top%20dollar%20just%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20Handshake%2C%20a%20platform%20where%20students%20can%20look%20for%20work%2C%20suggests%20a%20cooler%20demand%20for%20software%20developers%20or%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%2029%25%20decline%20in%20software%20developer%2Fengineer%20jobs%20created%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20Handshake%20network%20when%20comparing%20the%20period%20between%20June%202023%20and%20May%202024%20to%20the%20year%20before%2C%20Randy%20Tarnowski%2C%20senior%20manager%20of%20research%20and%20education%20insights%20at%20Handshake%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarnowski%20said%20that%20software%20engineering%20roles%20%26quot%3Breceived%20a%20large%20share%20of%202024%20computer%20science%20graduates'%20applications%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20share%20of%20applications%20has%20fallen%20by%20a%20few%20percentage%20points%20from%20the%20class%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20software%20engineering%20roles%2C%20the%20class%20of%202024%20computer%20science%20grads%20are%20submitting%20more%20of%20their%20applications%20to%20other%20roles%2C%20including%20data%20science%20and%20analysts%2C%20computer%20hardware%2C%20information%20security%2C%20computer%20systems%20engineering%2C%20and%20financial%20and%20investment%20analysts%20roles%2C%26quot%3B%20Tarnowski%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20people%20making%20job%20decisions%20amid%20the%20strong%20but%20cooler%20job%20market%2C%20Bunker%20suggested%20thinking%20about%20long-term%20prospects%20instead%20of%20simply%20how%20demand%20is%20looking%20at%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%2C%20a%20sector%20might%20not%20be%20%26quot%3Bas%20flashy%26quot%3B%20or%20offer%20as%20great%20of%20compensation%20as%20it%20had%20been.%20However%2C%20Bunker%20added%20some%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bshine%20might%20have%20come%20off%20some%20of%20these%20jobs%2C%20but%20they're%20still%20well%20paying%20and%20have%20a%20good%20long-term%20outlook.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20made%20a%20career%20change%20from%20or%20to%20software%20development%20or%20another%20tech%20job%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20to%20share%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emhoff%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-software-developers-job-seekers-high-paying-work-opportunities-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719048722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66758b80423319f0c3725267%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com