n%20so%20traumatic%2C%20especially%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20it's%20been%20really%2C%20really%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221243%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Leandro%20Pucci%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66748deb886e840164be8ae8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22932%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeandro%20Pucci.%3Cp%3ELeandro%20Pucci%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20defrauded%20borrowers%20like%20Pucci%20are%20eligible%20to%20apply%20for%20relief%20from%20private%20lenders%2C%20Navient's%20application%20for%20the%20relief%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnavient.com%2Floan-servicing%2Fprivate-student-loans%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20yet%20publicly%20available%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Even%20if%20a%20borrower%20manages%20to%20get%20the%20application%2C%20it%20can%20take%20hours%20to%20fill%20out%20and%20still%20result%20in%20a%20denial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20larger%20issue%20at%20play%20extends%20far%20beyond%20Navient.%20As%20millions%20of%20Americans%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstories-of-student-loan-debt-hamster-wheel-borrowers-cant-escape-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20struggle%20with%20student-debt%20loads%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20some%20of%20them%20being%20forced%20to%20make%20payments%20on%20loans%20for%20schools%20accused%20of%20fraud%20that%20did%20not%20deliver%20on%20their%20promises.%20While%20the%20Education%20Department%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-cancellation-payment-pause-borrowers-disabilities-defrauded-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaken%20a%20range%20of%20steps%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20cancel%20student%20debt%20for%20borrowers%20who%20went%20to%20schools%20it%20found%20guilty%20of%20fraud%2C%20those%20with%20private%20loans%20do%20not%20qualify%20for%20the%20same%20relief.%20The%20lender%2C%20instead%2C%20can%20decide%20how%20it%20wants%20to%20craft%20a%20relief%20process%2C%20if%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2200fc56f2-0583-420d-a037-4f8246e44d30%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelief%20is%20'still%20in%20its%20early%20stages'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%20wants%20answers.%20In%20April%2C%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felizabeth-warren-cancel-student-debt-borrowers-transfer-navient-to-mohela-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esent%20an%20inquiry%20to%20Navient%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20process%20and%20its%20responsibility%20to%20discharge%20fraudulent%20loans%20under%20a%20consumer%20protection%20tool%20known%20as%20the%20Holder%20Rule.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20Navient%20spokesperson%20referred%20BI%20to%20excerpts%20from%20the%20company's%20response%20to%20Warren%2C%20which%20stated%20that%20the%20discharge%20process%20is%20%26quot%3Bstill%20in%20its%20early%20stages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20this%20enhanced%20process%2C%20we%20have%20started%20to%20communicate%20to%20borrowers%20who%20may%20qualify.%20As%20the%20process%20continues%20to%20roll%20out%2C%20we%20expect%20that%20more%20borrowers%20will%20submit%20applications%2C%20leading%20to%20increased%20levels%20of%20cancellation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20told%20Warren.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavient%20said%20that%20it%20increased%20its%20reserves%20by%20%2435%20million%20in%20anticipation%20of%20relieving%20debt%20for%20defrauded%20borrowers%2C%20and%20it's%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20addressing%20valid%20school%20misconduct%20claims%26quot%3B%20to%20fulfill%20its%20responsibility%20under%20the%20Holder%20Rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20told%20Warren%20that%20%26quot%3Bin%20light%20of%20the%20circumstances%20of%20some%20private%20loan%20borrowers%20who%20attended%20certain%20for-profit%20colleges%20%E2%80%A6%20particularly%20those%20borrowers%20who%20suffered%20a%20negative%20impact%20from%20school%20closures%20or%20false%20promises%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20would%20be%20appropriate%20to%20develop%20a%20discharge%20process%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20the%20federal%20government%20for%20defrauded%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Navient%20promises%20that%20more%20borrowers%20will%20gain%20access%20to%20relief%20through%20the%20new%20application%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20clarity%20surrounding%20the%20timeline%20can%20impose%20a%20financial%20burden%20on%20those%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPucci%20said%20he%20obtained%20an%20application%20after%20filing%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Consumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%20in%20April%2C%20and%20just%20two%20weeks%20later%2C%20he%20received%20a%20denial%20from%20Navient.%20It%20stated%20that%20while%20Navient%20%26quot%3Bcarefully%20considers%20a%20variety%20of%20factors%20in%20determining%20whether%20a%20private%20loan%20should%20be%20discharged%20based%20on%20school%20misconduct%2C%26quot%3B%20Pucci%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20requirements.%20Since%20then%2C%20he's%20filed%20another%20complaint%20with%20the%20CFPB%20but%20has%20yet%20to%20get%20a%20clear%20reason%20as%20to%20why%20he%20was%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CFPB's%20Private%20Education%20Loan%20Ombudsman%20Julia%20Barnard%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bfor%20years%2C%20my%20office%20has%20heard%20from%20frustrated%20victims%20of%20predatory%20schools%20who%20are%20now%20struggling%20to%20get%20their%20private%20lender%20to%20cancel%20their%20fraudulent%20loans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20key%20measure%20of%20a%20relief%20process%20is%20whether%20qualifying%20borrowers%20get%20their%20fraudulent%20loans%20cancelled%2C%26quot%3B%20Barnard%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20office%20(and%20the%20CFPB%20more%20generally)%20is%20watching%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20student%20borrowers%20get%20appropriate%20relief%20and%20we%20will%20step%20in%20to%20help%20where%20we%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPucci%20said%20he%20cannot%20afford%20to%20pay%20off%20his%20private%20loans%20for%20much%20longer%2C%20but%20he%20doesn't%20know%20what%20else%20he%20can%20do%20aside%20from%20wait%20and%20hope%20that%20Navient%20will%20eventually%20give%20him%20the%20same%20relief%20the%20government%20already%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20made%20my%20decisions.%20I%20took%20my%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20Pucci%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20all%20the%20investments%20I%20need%20to%20do%20for%20my%20own%20business%20are%20impossible.%20I%20can%20forget%20about%20buying%20anything%20anymore%20because%20of%20how%20much%20I%20have%20to%20pay%20Navient.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225426efea-9491-4d49-8751-dccd660dff66%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'I've%20spent%20so%20much%20time%20feeling%20so%20alone%20and%20isolated'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETheresa%20Christman's%20story%20is%20similar%20to%20Pucci's.%20The%20now%2040-year-old%20attended%20the%20for-profit%20International%20Academy%20of%20Design%20and%20Technology%2C%20which%20was%20included%20in%20the%202022%20Sweet%20v.%20Cardona%20settlement%20that%20discharged%20student%20loans%20for%20federal%20borrowers%20who%20attended%20a%20long%20list%20of%20schools.%20However%2C%20she%20still%20has%20about%20%2422%2C000%20in%20private%20student%20loans%20serviced%20by%20Navient%20that%20she%20can't%20shake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20%24400%20a%20month%20payment%20was%20hard%2C%20especially%20when%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20eat%20or%20pay%20my%20bills%20for%20a%20really%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Christman%20told%20BI.%20She%20said%20she%20had%20to%20forgo%20car%20insurance%2C%20live%20on%20food%20stamps%2C%20and%20drop%20out%20of%20school%20so%20she%20could%20work%20full%20time.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20still%20only%20bringing%20in%20%2411%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20I%20was%20in%20California%2C%20which%20is%20not%20cheap.%20So%20it%20was%20hard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Theresa%20Christman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66748e28886e840164be8b14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETheresa%20Christman%3Cp%3ETheresa%20Christman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20filing%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20CFPB%2C%20Christman%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20she%20received%20the%20school%20misconduct%20discharge%20application%20from%20Navient%20%E2%80%94%20but%20due%20to%20the%20lengthy%20application%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20proof%20required%2C%20she%20hasn't%20had%20the%20time%20to%20put%20it%20together%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20each%20section%2C%20I%20am%20writing%20pages%20and%20pages%20and%20pages%20for%20each%20answer.%20So%20it's%20taking%20me%20a%20really%20long%20time%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Christman%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20give%20Navient%20any%20reason%20to%20deny%20my%20claim.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Project%20on%20Predatory%20Student%20Lending%20%E2%80%94%20an%20advocacy%20group%20working%20to%20help%20defrauded%20borrowers%20%E2%80%94%20launched%20an%20awareness%20campaign%20earlier%20in%20June%20to%20make%20borrowers%20aware%20of%20Navient's%20discharge%20application%2C%20including%20an%20example%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F62d6e418e8d8517940207135%2Ft%2F664e4ce0340ea96a0aa70c72%2F1716407521054%2FNavient%2BSchool%2BMisconduct%2BApplication.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblank%2012-page%20application%3C%2Fa%3E%20borrowers%20are%20required%20to%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEileen%20Connor%2C%20director%20of%20PPSL%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20process%20%26quot%3Bis%20really%20opaque%26quot%3B%20for%20borrowers%2C%20and%20it's%20forcing%20them%20to%20jump%20through%20unnecessary%20hurdles%20to%20get%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20Navient's%20process%2C%20most%20federal%20borrowers%20%26quot%3Bhaven't%20had%20to%20apply%20at%20all%20because%20the%20department%20has%20said%20that%20they%20have%20enough%20information%20in%20their%20possession%20to%20know%20that%20there%20was%20a%20widespread%20pattern%20that%20impacted%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20everybody%20who%20went%20to%20the%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20Connor%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20don't%20really%20know%20why%20that%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20same%20for%20these%20loans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20clarity%20going%20forward%20has%20left%20Christman%20in%20a%20limbo%20state%2C%20not%20knowing%20where%20she'll%20land%20once%20she%20submits%20her%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20spent%20so%20much%20time%20feeling%20so%20alone%20and%20isolated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20financial%20aspect%20has%20been%20absolutely%20devastating%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20affected%20my%20mental%20health%20so%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231d0e4cd-b6f5-45a4-aa05-499de0054e00%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'I%20can%20finally%20breathe%20again'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20borrowers%2C%20the%20time%20spent%20on%20the%20application%20paid%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVictoria%20Linssen%2C%2059%2C%20and%20Jennifer%20Nave%2C%2060%2C%20attended%20the%20for-profit%20Brooks%20Institute%20and%20DeVry%20University%2C%20respectively.%20Both%20received%20federal%20relief%20through%20the%20Sweet%20v.%20Cardona%20settlement%20and%20then%20struggled%20to%20be%20free%20of%20their%20private%20debt%20through%20Navient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Linssen%20received%20the%20school%20misconduct%20discharge%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20slowly%20but%20surely%20made%20my%20way%20through%20it.%20I%20would%20say%20it%20took%20me%20somewhere%20between%20eight%20and%2012%20hours%20to%20fill%20it%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Linssen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20almost%20need%20to%20be%20your%20own%20attorney%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20figure%20it%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20confusion%20and%20misunderstanding%20about%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20included%2C%20and%20some%20students%20aren't%20properly%20following%20the%20directions%20and%20are%20getting%20declined.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Linssen's%20efforts%20paid%20off%20%E2%80%94%20she%20got%20%2470%2C000%20in%20private%20loans%20discharged%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20never%20fully%20recover%20from%20what%20happened%20to%20me.%20When%20I%20left%20Brooks%2C%20I%20was%20in%20so%20much%20debt%20that%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20get%20married.%20I%20was%20in%20deep%20humiliation%20and%20shame%20at%20the%20decisions%20that%20I%20had%20made%20that%20put%20me%20in%20so%20much%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Victoria%20Linssen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66748ee065f501a88180e75d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVictoria%20Linssen%3Cp%3EVictoria%20Linssen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPPSL%20encourages%20borrowers%20who%20are%20denied%20relief%20through%20Navient%20to%20continue%20filing%20complaints%20with%20the%20CFPB.%20Connor%20also%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20strengthening%20consumer%20protection%20laws%20not%20just%20for%20Navient%20but%20for%20the%20private%20lending%20industry%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20given%20that%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bdifferent%20rules%20when%20talking%20about%20the%20federal%20government%20versus%20a%20private%20actor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinssen%20can%20now%20finally%20start%20to%20see%20a%20future%20that%20doesn't%20include%20any%20student%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20only%20just%20now%20in%20the%20place%20where%20I%20can%20finally%20breathe%20again%20and%20start%20feeling%20like%20a%20normal%20human%20being%20and%20start%20planning%20for%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20that%20tiny%2C%20tiny%20spotlight%20of%20hope%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20really%20long%20tunnel%20that%20I%20may%20be%20able%20to%20retire%20or%20have%20a%20life%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nave%20also%20eventually%20got%20her%20private%20loans%20relieved%20after%20filing%20complaints%20with%20the%20CFPB%2C%20she%20doesn't%20understand%20why%20it%20has%20to%20be%20this%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20I'm%20trying%20to%20prove%20to%20them%20something%20they%20already%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20Nave%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20took%20me%20seven%20hours%20to%20fill%20out%2C%20and%20it's%20very%20confusing%2C%20so%20many%20students%20are%20afraid%20of%20answering%20these%20questions%20because%20they're%20not%20exactly%20sure%20what%20is%20being%20asked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221611%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jennifer%20Nave%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66748f1865f501a88180e7a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221208%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJennifer%20Nave.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Nave%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2014%2C%20Nave%20was%20shocked%20to%20see%20her%20efforts%20paid%20off%20%E2%80%94%20Navient%20effectively%20discharged%20her%20remaining%20balance%20after%20over%20a%20decade%20of%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20Eucker%2C%2038%2C%20hasn't%20been%20so%20lucky.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEucker%20attended%20the%20Brooks%20Institute%20and%20graduated%20with%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%20commercial%20photography%20in%202008.%20While%20he%20was%20fortunate%20to%20find%20employment%20in%20the%20field%2C%20he%20wasn't%20making%20as%20much%20as%20he%20was%20promised%20%E2%80%94%20so%20he%20struggled%20to%20manage%20his%20student-loan%20payments%20while%20also%20juggling%20rent%20and%20other%20basic%20necessities%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20huge%20financial%20burden.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20has%20been%20the%20case%20with%20many%20other%20borrowers%2C%20Eucker%20received%20a%20school%20misconduct%20discharge%20application%20after%20filing%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20CFPB.%20He%20submitted%20his%20application%20%E2%80%94%20over%20200%20pages%20%E2%80%94%20to%20Navient%20in%20early%20May%2C%20and%20in%20June%2C%20he%20received%20a%20denial.%20The%20reason%20was%20the%20exact%20same%20as%20the%20one%20Pucci%20received%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20do%20not%20meet%20the%20requirements%20for%20discharge%20based%20on%20misconduct%20by%20your%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Navient%20said%20it's%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20all%20borrowers%20who%20qualify%20for%20relief%20receive%20it%2C%20it%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20specific%20criteria%20it%20uses%20to%20evaluate%20borrowers'%20applications%20%E2%80%94%20rather%20saying%20that%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20evaluate%20and%20update%20the%20process%20as%20it%20makes%20sense.%20But%20it's%20leaving%20borrowers%20like%20Eucker%20and%20Pucci%20without%20any%20information%20on%20how%20to%20proceed%2C%20keeping%20them%20saddled%20with%20debt%20they're%20struggling%20to%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20get%20your%20hopes%20up%2C%20and%20it%20seems%20like%20this%20program%20might%20actually%20work.%20But%20then%20I%20got%20that%20letter%20that%20said%20I%20didn't%20qualify%2C%20and%20it%20ruined%20my%20entire%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Eucker%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20this%20big%20letdown%2C%20once%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-defrauded-borrowers-navient-borrower-defense-relief-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719047821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66748f83886e840164be8d20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-defrauded-borrowers-navient-bor