20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.gadgets360cdn.com%2Flarge%2Fpanchayat_season_2_1651209306392.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt'd%20be%20a%20clich%C3%A9%C2%A0to%20recognise%20the%20recent%20phenomenon%20of%20filming%20%26quot%3Breal%26quot%3B%20India%20for%20%26quot%3Breal%26quot%3B%20Indians%2C%20if%20one%20were%20to%20go%20by%20that%20old%20adage%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%20lives%20in%20its%20villages%26quot%3B.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20third%20season%20of%20Amazon%20Prime's%20highly%20loved%20web%20series%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fjitendra-kumar-on-rumours-of-being-the-highest-paid-actor-of-panchayat-3-nothing-good-comes-out-of-the-discussion-5865184%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20premiered%20with%20great%20fanfare.%20Thus%20far%2C%20the%20series%20seems%20to%20have%20delivered%20on%20its%20promises%2C%20with%20its%20viewership%20only%20increasing.%20However%2C%20as%20some%20critics%20argue%2C%20the%20once-beloved%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwas-panchayat-shot-in-rajasthans-phulera-the-answer-is-5822054%5C%22%3EPhulera%20Gaon%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20of%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20got%20embroiled%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20political%20maelstrom%26quot%3B%2C%20challenging%20the%20show's%20earlier%20vibe%2C%20as%20journalist%20Vibha%20Maru%20puts%20it.%20She%20notes%20that%20the%20'Phul'%20of%20Phulera%20has%20lost%20its%20lustre.%20Maru's%20observation%20of%20the%20fading%20Malgudi%20Days-like%20simplicity%20of%20Phulera%20and%20Phakoli%20Bazaar%20gains%20credence%20considering%20the%20growing%20reliance%20of%20OTT%20platforms%20on%20big%20data%20to%20cater%20to%20specific%20audience%20preferences%20and%20perpetuate%20certain%20aesthetics%20or%20predispositions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Layered%20Picture%20Of%2021st-Century%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20initially%20appeared%20as%20a%20timeless%20Indian%20tale%20of%20Abhishek%20(played%20by%20Jitendra%20Kumar)%2C%20an%20IIM%20aspirant-turned-village%20secretary%2C%20and%20his%20earnest%20companion%20Vikas%20(Chandan%20Roy)%2C%20supported%20by%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Dubey%20(Raghubir%20Yadav)%2C%20Manju%20Devi%20(Neena%20Gupta)%2C%20Prahlad%20Pandey%20(Faisal%20Malik)%2C%20Rinki%20(Sanvikaa)%2C%20Bhushan%20(Durgesh%20Kumar)%2C%20Binod%20(Ashok%20Pathak)%2C%20and%20others%2C%20has%20now%20evolved%20into%20a%20narrative%20encompassing%20social%2C%20political%2C%20and%20gender%20complexities%20unique%20to%2021st-century%20suburban%20India.%20The%20question%20remains%3A%20how%20idyllic%20is%20the%20India%20that%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20portrays%20on%20screen%2C%20and%20how%20credible%20is%20the%20transformation%20of%20its%20fictional%20village%20to%20a%20potentially%20darker%20reality%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fwas-panchayat-shot-in-rajasthans-phulera-the-answer-is-5822054%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Was%20Panchayat%20Shot%20In%20Rajasthan's%20Phulera%3F%20The%20Answer%20Is...%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20series'%20broad%20appeal%2C%20opinions%20naturally%20vary.%20Political%20scientist%20and%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences%20professor%20Ashwani%20Kumar%20suggests%20that%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20challenges%20%26quot%3Bthe%20endurable%20images%20of%20primordial%20rural%20reality%20in%20the%20classic%20%3Cem%3EDo%20Bigha%20Zamin%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1953)%2C%20%3Cem%3EPather%20Panchali%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1955)%20or%20%3Cem%3EMother%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1957)%26quot%3B.%20Instead%2C%20it%20presents%20a%20%26quot%3Bdelightful%20and%20seductive%20celluloid%20ethnography%20of%20vernacular%20cosmopolitanism%20in%20Indian%20villages%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESteering%20clear%20of%20stereotypical%2C%20crude%2C%20or%20unrealistically%20utopian%20portrayals%20of%20rural%20life%2C%20Phulera%20in%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20offers%20a%20cinematic%20journey%20that%20Ashis%20Nandy%20describes%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btime%20travel%20to%20a%20potential%20self%26quot%3B%20within%20an%20Indian%20village%2C%20where%20genuine%20Indian%20experiences%20confront%20contrived%2C%20pseudo%20depictions%20of%20the%20village.%20Rural%20cultural%20entrepreneur%20and%20founder%20of%20banglanatak.com%2C%20Amitava%20Bhattacharjee%2C%20concurs%20on%20the%20theme%20of%20representative%20realism%2C%20noting%20that%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20authentically%20portrays%20rural%20life%2C%20striking%20a%20balance%20by%20showcasing%20both%20its%20charms%20and%20its%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BLike%20Doordarshan%20From%20Many%20Moons%20Ago%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20the%20release%20of%20Season%203%2C%20these%20viewpoints%20largely%20encapsulated%20critical%20perspectives%20on%20the%20series.%20According%20to%20Bhattacharjee%2C%20until%20the%20previous%20season%2C%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20explored%20the%20daily%20lives%20of%20simple%20villagers%2C%20focusing%20on%20their%20interactions%20and%20challenges%20through%20%26quot%3Bsituational%20comedy%26quot%3B%2C%20highlighting%20rural%20bureaucracy's%20absurdities%20and%20inefficiencies.%20The%20narrative%20centred%20on%20a%20city%20graduate's%20journey%20of%20getting%20used%20to%20village%20life.%20Bhattacharjee%20emphasised%20that%20the%20series'%20triumph%20lay%20not%20merely%20in%20its%20depiction%20of%20rural%20India%20but%20in%20revitalising%20a%20rustic%20genre%20devoid%20of%20guns%2C%20crime%2C%20and%20bloodshed.%20It%20almost%20reminded%20one%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Doordarshan%20serials%20from%20many%20moons%20ago%26quot%3B%2C%20says%20Mumbai-and-Delhi-based%20author%20and%20entrepreneur%2C%20Shriti%20Tyagi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fpanchayat-actor-durgesh-kumar-aka-bhushan-on-his-struggling-days-suffered-depression-twice-in-11-years-5808565%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ci%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0Actor%20Durgesh%20Kumar%20AKA%20Bhushan%20On%20His%20Struggling%20Days%3A%20%26quot%3BSuffered%20Depression%20Twice%20In%2011%20Years%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sentiment%20is%20echoed%20by%20filmmaker%20and%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20journalist%20Gautam%20Singh%2C%20who%20praises%20the%20series%20for%20its%20sharp%20portrayal%20of%20rural%20India's%20humour%20and%20authenticity%2C%20particularly%20in%20capturing%20the%20nuances%20of%20%26quot%3Bpurvanchali%20boli%26quot%3B%20or%20dialects%20from%20Eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20including%20the%20Ballia%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETheatre%20vs%20OTT%20Audiences%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Singh%20cautions%20that%20no%20single%20show%20can%20fully%20capture%20the%20diversity%20of%20rural%20setting.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20consider%20the%20larger%20political%20contexts%20shaping%20OTT%20series%20like%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Harish%20Wankhede%2C%20Professor%20of%20Political%20Science%20at%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20observes%20that%20a%20stylised%20urban%20perspective%20shapes%20new%20representations%20of%20rural%20and%20suburban%20India.%20He%20further%20adds%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20a%20clear%20bifurcation%20between%20theatre-going%20viewership%20sensibilities%20and%20OTT%20aesthetics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20of%20these%20ostensibly%20realistic%20portrayals%20of%20a%20newly%20mainstreamed%20rural%20India%2C%20caste%20complexities%20remain%20neglected%2C%20laments%20Wankhede.%20Rittvika%20Singh%2C%20Professor%20of%20English%20at%20IGNOU%2C%20further%20observes%20that%20OTT%20platforms%20cater%20to%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20social%20elite%20and%20have%20failed%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20deeply%20entrenched%20caste%20dynamics.%20%26quot%3BThe%20casual%20erasure%20of%20caste%20-%20given%20that%20all%20the%20main%20characters%20of%20the%20series%20hail%20from%20a%20particular%20caste%20-%20works%20as%20a%20tried%20and%20tested%20way%20of%20mainstream%20viewing%20to%20avoid%20dealing%20with%20difficult%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Ffaisal-malik-aka-prahlad-cha-gets-candid-about-his-preparation-for-panchayat-5836842%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Faisal%20Malik%20On%20The%20Emotional%20Scene%20In%C2%A0%3Ci%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fi%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BDidn't%20Think%20I%20Would%20Be%20Able%20To%20Pull%20It%20Off%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20observation%20resonates%20with%20Jitendra%20Kumar's%20acknowledgement%20that%20OTT%20platforms%20attract%20a%20significant%20following%20among%20urban%20young%20adults%2C%20who%20eagerly%20wait%20to%20return%20home%20to%20their%20favourite%20web%20series%20after%20corporate%20work%20hours%2C%20where%20'authenticity'%20becomes%20both%20a%20buzzword%20and%20a%20contested%20concept.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERittvika%20Singh%20observes%20that%20while%20Season%201%20of%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20authentically%20portrayed%20rural%20life%2C%20its%20realism%20has%20waned%20since%20then.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20questions%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20panchayat%20election%20is%20fought%20on%20caste%20lines%20(as%20it%20often%20is%20in%20reality)%3F%20Would%20the%20Pradhan%20have%20the%20same%20circle%20of%20associates%20if%20he%20weren't%20from%20a%20privileged%20caste%3F%20Would%20he%20accept%20a%20secretary%20from%20a%20different%20caste%3F%20Imagining%20a%20comedy%20on%20screen%20that%20is%20not%20only%20emotionally%20but%20also%20politically%20aware%20of%20village%20social%20dynamics%20would%20be%20more%20intriguing.%26quot%3B%20Bhattacharjee%20concurs%2C%20suggesting%20that%20Panchayat%20could%20have%20delved%20into%20caste%20dynamics%2C%20gender%20inequality%2C%20and%20economic%20disparities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20Panchayat%20Not%20Be%20A%20Victim%20Of%20Its%20Success%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20evident%20shortcomings%20in%20its%20political%20narrative%20and%20the%20complex%20politics%20surrounding%20its%20consumption%20and%20incidental%20learning%2C%20the%20question%2C%20as%20Kumar%20advises%2C%20is%20this%3A%20should%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20become%20a%20victim%20of%20its%20success%3F%20The%20show%20deserves%20recognition%20for%20what%20it%20represents%3A%20an%20India%20that%20was%20not%20considered%20worthy%20of%20mainstream%20portrayal%20until%20a%20decade%20ago.%20Rather%20than%20solely%20interrogating%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20one%20should%20consider%20what%20prompts%20the%20urban%20gaze%20to%20localise%20themes%20of%20frustration%2C%20aggression%2C%20and%20violence%20in%20smaller%20towns%20and%20the%20so-deemed%20%26quot%3Bless%20civilised%26quot%3B%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20and%20why%20cities%20like%20Noida%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Bangalore%20or%20Mumbai%20are%20usually%20spared%20this%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Feverywhere-i-go-people-call-me-pradhan-ji-raghubir-yadav-on-panchayat-success-5867329%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Raghubir%20Yadav%20On%20The%C2%A0%3Ci%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0Effect%3A%20%26quot%3BEverywhere%20I%20Go%2C%20People%20Call%20Me%20Pradhan%C2%A0%3Ci%3EJi%3C%2Fi%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20noticeable%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20screenwriters%20and%20filmmakers%20from%20cosmopolitan%20cities%20dedicated%20to%20crafting%20exotic%20narratives%20of%20rural%20India%2C%20especially%20following%20the%20success%20of%20Anurag%20Kashyap's%20Gangs%20of%20Wasseypur%20(2012)%20duology.%20One%20might%20even%20l