et%20angry%20about%20everything.%20People%20talk%20to%20him%20carefully.%20When%20I%20speak%20to%20him%2C%20I%20keep%20within%20my%20limits.%20Darshan%20has%20openly%20admitted%20in%20interviews%20that%20he%20has%20anger%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%2C%20however%2C%20said%20she%20wasn't%20aware%20of%20Darshan's%20relationship%20with%20Pavithra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rai%20also%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20actor's%20wife%20and%2015-year-old%20son%2C%20who%20are%20facing%20hate%20comments%20online%2C%20in%20an%20Instagram%20post%20earlier%20this%20week.%20Pointing%20out%20that%20Darshan%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20convicted%2C%20she%20said%20the%20law%20will%20take%20its%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERenuka%20Swamy%2C%20a%2033-year-old%20resident%20of%20Chitradurga%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20was%20allegedly%20tortured%20and%20killed%20by%20Darshan%20and%20his%20fans%20after%20they%20kidnapped%20him%20from%20his%20home%20on%20June%208.%20Next%20morning%2C%20his%20body%20was%20found%20in%20a%20drain%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20autopsy%20found%2015%20wounds%20on%20his%20body%20and%20revealed%20that%20he%20died%20of%20shock%20and%20haemorrhage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDarshan%2C%20a%20popular%20name%20in%20the%20Kannada%20film%20industry%2C%20was%20arrested%20two%20days%20later%20from%20his%20Mysuru%20farmhouse.%20Pavithra%2C%20his%20co-star%2C%20has%20been%20named%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20and%20is%20also%20in%20custody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor%20Sanjjanaa%20Galrani%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20with%20him%2C%20had%20earlier%20told%20NDTV%20that%20he%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bdemigod%20figure%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Kannada%20industry%20and%20that%20his%20arrest%20marked%20a%20%26quot%3Bblack%20day%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20artistes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Darshan's%20%26quot%3Btemperamental%20nature%26quot%3B%20and%20past%20controversies%2C%20Ms%20Galrani%20had%20defended%20him%20saying%20he%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bsoft-spoken%20gentleman%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20respectful%20and%20gentle%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20person%20being%20spoken%20about%20in%20the%20news%20and%20the%20person%20that%20I%20know%20feel%20like%20two%20different%20personalities%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719036720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fpaq6o0ag_anusha-rai-darshan_625x300_22_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarshan-thoogudeepa-renuka-swamy-murder-case-darshan-has-anger-issues-i-speak-to-him-within-my-limits-actor-anusha-rai-5943854%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kannada%20actor%20Darshan%20Thoogudeepa%20has%20anger%20issues%2C%20a%20co-star%20has%20claimed%20amid%20allegations%20that%20he%20got%20a%20man%20killed%20for%20posting%20lewd%20comments%20about%20his%20co-star%20Pavithra%20Gowda.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarshan-thoogudeepa-renuka-swamy-murder-case-darshan-has-anger-issues-i-speak-to-him-within-my-limits-actor-anusha-rai-5943854%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarshan-thoogudeepa-renuka-swamy-murder-case-darshan-has-anger-issues-i-speak-to-him-within-my-limits-actor-anusha-rai-5943854%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdarshan-thoogudeepa-renuka-swamy-murder-case-darshan-has-anger-issues-i-speak-to-him-within-my-limits-actor-anusha-rai-5943854%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Likely%20Yemen%20Houthi%20rebel%20attack%20targets%20ship%20in%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%20as%20Eisenhower%20reportedly%20heads%20home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719036320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111183978%2Cimgsize-714464.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimes