in%20Mumbai.%20The%20pre-wedding%20festivities%20are%20in%20full%20swing%2C%20with%20both%20families%20deeply%20involved%20in%20the%20celebrations.%20Shatrughan%20Sinha's%20iconic%20home%2C%20a%20multi-storey%20building%20named%20Ramayan%20in%20Juhu%2C%20has%20been%20adorned%20with%20decorative%20lights%2C%20capturing%20everyone's%20attention%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Minister%20Explains%20Why%20NEET%20Exam%20Is%20Not%20Cancelled%20Despite%20Paper%20Leak%20Probe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20opted%20to%20not%20cancel%20the%20medical%20entrance%20examination%20NEET%2C%20despite%20a%20raging%20controversy%20and%20an%20ongoing%20investigation%20of%20the%20paper%20being%20leaked%20a%20day%20before%20the%20exam.%20Explaining%20their%20stand%2C%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20said%20that%20the%20leak%20affected%20only%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20students%2C%20contrasting%20sharply%20with%20previous%20incidents%20in%202004%20and%202015%20where%20broader%20leaks%20led%20to%20exam%20cancellations.%20He%20said%20that%20cancelling%20the%20exam%20would%20affect%20lakhs%20of%20students%20who%20cleared%20the%20examination%20rightfully.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20case%20is%20being%20heard%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20any%20decision%20taken%20by%20the%20court%20will%20be%20the%20final%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20row%20erupted%20after%2067%20students%20scored%20a%20perfect%20720%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam%2C%20and%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20clarified%20that%20they%20had%20given%20grace%20marks%20to%20some%20students%20due%20to%20a%20wrong%20question%20and%20delay%20in%20candidates%20getting%20the%20question%20paper%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2024%20lakh%20students%20participated%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20examination%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20programs%2C%20administered%20by%20the%20NTA%2C%20held%20on%20May%205.%20The%20results%20were%20released%20ahead%20of%20schedule%20on%20June%204.%20However%2C%20controversy%20arose%20with%20claims%20of%20a%20question%20paper%20leak%20and%20the%20awarding%20of%20grace%20marks%20to%20more%20than%201%2C500%20students%2C%20leading%20to%20widespread%20protests%20and%20legal%20actions%2C%20including%20cases%20filed%20in%20various%20courts%2C%20notably%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20has%20strongly%20criticised%20the%20NTA's%20handling%20of%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20refused%20to%20cancel%20the%20exam%20as%20the%20leak%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20localised%20and%20only%20a%20couple%20of%20students%20from%20Bihar%20were%20the%20beneficiaries.%20A%20student%20and%20three%20other%20accused%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20are%20being%20questioned%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerming%20the%20leak%20of%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam's%20question%20paper%20an%20%26quot%3Binstitutional%20failure%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said%20the%20government%20will%20constitute%20a%20high-level%20panel%20to%20look%20into%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20agency%2C%20but%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20cancel%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20unfair%20to%20hold%20hostage%20the%20career%20of%20those%20candidates%20who%20have%20rightfully%20cleared%20the%20exam%20because%20of%20some%20isolated%20incidents%20of%20malpractice%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20constant%20touch%20with%20the%20Bihar%20Police.%20We%20have%20sought%20a%20report%20from%20them.%20Once%20we%20have%20it%2C%20we%20will%20decide%20the%20future%20course%20of%20action.%20I%20take%20full%20responsibility%20and%20anomalies%20in%20the%20system%20will%20be%20rectified.%20Let%20us%20have%20faith%20in%20our%20systems%20and%20no%20irregularities%20or%20malpractices%20will%20be%20tolerated%20by%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20appealed%20to%20the%20opposition%20parties%20not%20to%20politicise%20the%20issue%20and%20said%20strict%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20found%20guilty%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Btop%26quot%3B%20officials%20of%20the%20NTA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20has%20expedited%20its%20response%20to%20the%20issue%2C%20acknowledging%20concerns%20over%20grace%20marks%20and%20affirming%20that%20these%20have%20already%20been%20appropriately%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719035760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Frda45iuc_neet-exam-protest_625x300_22_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-minister-explains-why-neet-exam-is-not-cancelled-despite-paper-leak-probe-5943999%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20opted%20to%20not%20cancel%20the%20medical%20entrance%20examination%20NEET%2C%20despite%20a%20raging%20controversy%20and%20an%20ongoing%20investigation%20of%20the%20paper%20being%20leaked%20a%20day%20before%20the%20exam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-minister-explains-why-neet-exam-is-not-cancelled-despite-paper-leak-probe-5943999%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-minister-explains-why-neet-exam-is-not-cancelled-despite-paper-leak-probe-5943999%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-minister-explains-why-neet-exam-is-not-cancelled-despite-paper-leak-probe-5943999%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ananya%20Panday%20voiced%20Inside%20Out%202%20nears%2013%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A171903