Zaman%2C%20and%20Muhammad%20Amir%20were%20among%20those%20who%20had%20family%20members%20travelling%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabar%2C%20who%20is%20not%20married%2C%20had%20his%20father%2C%20mother%20and%20brothers%20staying%20in%20the%20team%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20extra%20expenses%20incurred%20on%20having%20families%20is%20obviously%20paid%20by%20players%20but%20having%20family%20members%20around%20does%20hit%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%2060%20rooms%20were%20booked%20where%20the%20team%20stayed%20to%20accommodate%20the%20other%20people%20travelling%20with%20the%20team.%20The%20environment%20was%20a%20family%20one%20with%20take-away%20dinners%20and%20outings%20being%20the%20norm%20for%20some%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Test%20wicketkeeper%2C%20Atiq%20uz%20Zaman%20said%20he%20could%20understand%20the%20players'%20need%20to%20have%20their%20families%20with%20them%20on%20low-profile%20or%20bilateral%20tours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20a%20major%20event%20like%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20the%20PCB%20should%20not%20have%20allowed%20such%20a%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20World%20Cup%2C%20no%20families%20should%20have%20been%20allowed%20as%20the%20players%20needed%20to%20focus%20on%20their%20cricket.%20When%20you%20have%20families%20with%20you%20then%20a%20player's%20attention%20and%20time%20is%20diverted%20from%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Zaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmir%20had%20also%20taken%20his%20personal%20trainer%20to%20the%20World%20Cup%20at%20his%20own%20expense%20despite%20the%20team%20having%20a%20foreign%20trainer%2C%20strength%20conditioning%20coach%2C%20physiotherapist%20and%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20report%20said%20that%20during%20training%20sessions%2C%20the%20left-arm%20pacer%20trained%20away%20from%20others%2C%20having%20taken%20permission%20from%20the%20board%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPCB%20mulls%20legal%20action%20against%20unverified%20reports%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20will%20be%20using%20a%20new%20defamation%20law%20by%20the%20Punjab%20government%20to%20go%20after%20digital%20or%20mainstream%20media%20who%20insinuate%20corruption%20by%20Pakistani%20players%20during%20the%20World%20Cup%20or%20make%20very%20personal%20remarks%20about%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20reliable%20source%20in%20the%20PCB%20said%20that%20the%20Board's%20legal%20department%20has%20already%20started%20working%20on%20possible%20notices%20under%20the%20new%20defamation%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20people%20will%20be%20asked%20to%20prove%20their%20allegations%20or%20face%20action%20under%20the%20new%20defamation%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Punjab%20assembly%20recently%20passed%20the%20bill%20related%20to%20digital%20media%20and%20defamation%20laws%20under%20which%20any%20digital%20journalist%20or%20media%20personality%20making%20unsubstantiated%20allegations%20or%20personal%20attacks%20on%20a%20public%20figure%20which%20put%20him%20in%20danger%20of%20public%20backlash%20can%20face%20a%20heavy%20fine%20and%20also%20time%20in%20jail%20if%20found%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20also%20states%20a%20decision%20has%20to%20come%20in%20six%20months%20and%20cases%20should%20not%20linger%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20after%20skipper%20Babar%20Azam%20was%20accused%20of%20accepting%20an%20expensive%20car%20as%20gift%20by%20YouTuber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719030240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F00ttlq2o_babar-azam-insta_625x300_21_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-c