0criticism%20from%20former%20players%20and%20fans%20because%20of%20their%20World%20Cup%20campaign.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbabar-azam-contemplating-legal-notice-to-counter-criticism-report-makes-big-claim-5943363%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbabar-azam-contemplating-legal-notice-to-counter-criticism-report-makes-big-claim-5943363%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbabar-azam-contemplating-legal-notice-to-counter-criticism-report-makes-big-claim-5943363%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20The%20New%20Law%20Aims%20To%20Curb%20Question%20Paper%20Leaks%20In%20Public%20Exams%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20introduced%20a%20strict%20law%20to%20curb%20paper%20leaks%20and%20cheating%20in%20public%20examinations%20amid%20a%20massive%20controversy%20over%20the%20NEET%20and%20UGC-NET%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Public%20Examinations%20(Prevention%20of%20Unfair%20Means)%20Act%2C%202024%20was%20notified%20Friday%20evening%20by%20the%20Ministry%20Of%20Personnel%2C%20Public%20Grievances%20and%20Pensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20important%20provisions%20in%20the%20law%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20law%20has%20provisions%20for%20at%20least%20three%20years%20imprisonment%20for%20those%20caught%20using%20unfair%20means%20during%20exams.%20It%20may%20be%20extended%20to%20five%20years%20and%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20fine%20may%20also%20be%20imposed%20on%20them.%20The%20jail%20term%20may%20be%20extended%20further%20if%20one%20fails%20to%20pay%20the%20fine.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bservice%20provider%26quot%3B%20-%20or%20testing%20agency%20-%20will%20face%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20a%20crore%20and%20a%20proportionate%20cost%20of%20examination%20shall%20also%20be%20recovered%20from%20them.%20They%20may%20also%20be%20barred%20from%20holding%20any%20public%20exam%20for%20four%20years%2C%20the%20law%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20law%20also%20provides%20for%20a%20jail%20term%20of%20three%20years%2C%20which%20may%20be%20extended%20up%20to%2010%20years%2C%20if%20anyone%20from%20the%20senior%20management%20is%20found%20involved.%20A%20fine%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20may%20also%20be%20imposed%20on%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20provisions%20of%20the%20law%20will%20not%20be%20applicable%20to%20a%20person%20who%20is%20able%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20offence%20was%20committed%20without%20his%20knowledge%20and%20that%20he%20tried%20his%20best%20to%20prevent%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhoever%20-%20be%20it%20a%20person%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Bservice%20provider%26quot%3B%20-%20commits%20an%20organised%20crime%20will%20face%20imprisonment%20of%20at%20least%20five%20years%2C%20which%20may%20be%20extended%20to%2010%20years%2C%20along%20with%20a%20fine%20of%20at%20least%20Rs%201%20crore%2C%20the%20law%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Eligibility-cum-Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%20and%20University%20Grants%20Commission-National%20Eligibility%20Test%20(UGC-NET)%2C%20two%20top%20public%20examinations%20that%20are%20taken%20by%20lakhs%20of%20Indians%20for%20careers%20in%20medical%20and%20academic%20courses%2C%20are%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20huge%20controversy%20that%20has%20seen%20students%20hitting%20the%20streets%20in%20the%20past%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2024%20lakh%20aspirants%20had%20taken%20the%20NEET%20exam%20on%20May%205%20for%20admission%20into%20medical%20colleges%20across%20India%2C%20but%20several%20irregularities%20surfaced%20when%20the%20results%20were%20declared%20on%20June%204.%20At%20least%20four%20men%20have%20confessed%20to%20paper%20leaks%20ahead%20of%20the%20NEET%20exam%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUGC-NET%20was%20cancelled%20on%20June%2019%2C%20a%20day%20after%20it%20was%20conducted%2C%20with%20the%20Education%20ministry%20stating%20exam%20integrity%20was%20compromised.%20The%20question%20paper%20for%20the%20exam%20was%20leaked%2048%20hours%20earlier%20and%20sold%20on%20the%20dark%20web%20and%20encrypted%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20CBI%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719028980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8kin8q6g_entrance-exam-generic_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-the-new-law-aims-to-curb-paper-leaks-cheating-in-public-exams-5943488%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20introduced%20a%20strict%20law%20to%20curb%20paper%20leaks%20and%20cheating%20in%20public%20examinations%20amid%20a%20massive%20controversy%20over%20the%20NEET%20and%20UGC-NET%20exams.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-the-new-law-aims-to-curb-paper-leaks-cheating-in-public-exams-5943488%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-the-new-law-aims-to-curb-paper-leaks-cheating-in-public-exams-5943488%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-the-new-law-aims-to-curb-paper-leaks-cheating-in-public-exams-5943488%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20states%20want%20to%20ban%20phones%20in%20schools.%20How%20would%20that%20work%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719028953000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Faf89%2Flive%2F6d8897d0-302b-11ef-b282-c78fceb523a5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fce99443qweno%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20schools%20are%20weighing%20smartphone%20bans%20as%20students%20struggle%20to%20socialise%20and%20face%20mental-health%20issues.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A51%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F