ial%20as%20it%20directly%20impacts%20the%20quantity%20of%20water%20we%20need.%20Drinking%20water%20and%20cooking%20water%20must%20be%20of%20high%20quality%20since%20they%20directly%20enter%20our%20bodies%20and%20affect%20our%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgreywater-1718806405.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Subhajit%20Mukherjee%20has%20been%20advocating%20reusing%20greywater%20and%20is%20also%20the%20founder%20of%20Mission%20Green%20Mumbai%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgreywater-1718806405.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgreywater-1718806405-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgreywater-1718806405-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgreywater-1718806405-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fgreywater-1718806405-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353543%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESubhajit%20Mukherjee%20has%20been%20advocating%20reusing%20greywater%20and%20is%20also%20the%20founder%20of%20Mission%20Green%20Mumbai.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%20recycled%20water%20can%20be%20a%20viable%20option%20for%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F123663%2Fwater-conservation-kadbanwadi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20water%20conservation%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20non-drinking%20purposes%2C%20such%20as%20mopping%20the%20floor%20or%20flushing%20toilets%2C%20where%20there%20is%20no%20direct%20personal%20contact%20with%20the%20water%2C%20using%20recycled%20greywater%20is%20a%20viable%20option%20that%20requires%20minimal%20effort.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecycled%20greywater%20is%20safe%20for%20use%20as%20it%20does%20not%20involve%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20human%20body%20nor%20is%20it%20used%20for%20consumption%2C%20hence%20not%20affecting%20our%20physical%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSpecial%20emphasis%20should%20be%20placed%20on%20toilet%20flushing%2C%20as%20in%20most%20urban%20areas%2C%2035%25%20of%20the%20freshwater%20supplied%20by%20the%20piped%20water%20system%20is%20wasted%20on%20flushing%20toilets%20every%20day.%20If%20we%20replace%20that%20with%20greywater%2C%20at%20least%2035%20percent%20fresh%20water%20will%20be%20saved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20such%20systems%2C%20contrary%20to%20public%20scepticism%20about%20cost%20and%20complexity%2C%20proves%20neither%20difficult%20to%20install%20nor%20expensive%2C%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20basic%20home%20setup%20for%20recycling%201%2C000%20litres%20of%20greywater%20can%20be%20established%20with%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20approximately%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20Moreover%2C%20larger%20facilities%20like%20housing%20complexes%20or%20educational%20institutions%20can%20implement%20extensive%20recycling%20systems%2C%20with%20costs%20not%20exceeding%20Rs%2020%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20systems%20not%20only%20recycle%20water%20but%20also%20allow%20for%20percolation%20into%20the%20ground%2C%20aiding%20groundwater%20recharge%20and%20helping%20mitigate%20urban%20heat%20island%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20system%20works%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGreywater%20filtration%20has%20various%20quality%20standards%20depending%20upon%20the%20reuse%20that%20we%20have%20focusing%20on.%20If%20we%20want%20to%20use%20it%20for%20flushing%20purposes%20we%20can%20have%20a%20simple%20sand%20filter%20which%20is%20a%20natural%20resource.%20However%2C%20if%20we%20want%20to%20use%20it%20for%20mopping%20floors%20or%20washing%20of%20car%20then%20we%20use%20a%205%20Micron%20filter%20which%20will%20filter%20out%20all%20the%20detergent%20and%20harmful%20oil%20from%20the%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternationally%2C%20nations%20like%20Dubai%20and%20Singapore%20have%20set%20precedents%20by%20filtering%20and%20repurposing%20sewage%20water%20for%20drinking.%20%E2%80%9CDrawing%20inspiration%20from%20such%20models%2C%20we%20should%20focus%20primarily%20on%20non-potable%20applications%20to%20ease%20into%20broader%20acceptance%20and%20implementation%20of%20water%20reuse%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20initial%20scepticism%20and%20hesitation%20among%20people%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20discuss%20greywater%20reutilisation%20with%20people%2C%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20they%20encounter%20are%20understanding%20what%20greywater%20is%20and%20the%20misconception%20that%20it%20is%20an%20expensive%20project%20requiring%20modern%20imported%20patented%20filters%20costing%20lakhs%20of%20rupees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20initial%20hesitance%20often%20encountered%20when%20introducing%20the%20concept%20of%20greywater%20reuse%2C%20the%20tangible%20benefits%20%E2%80%94%20both%20economic%20and%20environmental%20%E2%80%94%20quickly%20turn%20scepticism%20into%20motivation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20explain%20that%20it%20can%20be%20done%20for%20just%2020%2C000%20rupees%20or%20even%20less%2C%20they%20feel%20more%20motivated.%20Additionally%2C%20knowing%20that%20the%20system%20requires%20only%20a%2010%20by%2010%20feet%20space%20further%20encourages%20them.%20Ultimately%2C%20everyone%20facing%20water%20shortages%20today%20understands%20the%20importance%20of%20reusing%20water%2C%20and%20these%20clarifications%20make%20them%20more%20likely%20to%20implement%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345175%2Fhow-to-save-water-at-home-bengaluru-water-crisis-solution-dr-divya-sharma-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20greywater%20reutilisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20overcoming%20the%20hurdles%20of%20public%20perception%20and%20logistical%20application%2C%20it%20is%20a%20promising%20pathway%20to%20not%20just%20alleviating%20India%E2%80%99s%20water%20scarcity%2C%20but%20also%20setting%20a%20benchmark%20in%20sustainable%20water%20management%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20Pictures%20Credit%3A%20Subhajit%20Mukherjee)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718873595000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D353524%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Green%20activist%20Subhajit%20Mukherjee%20advocates%20for%20greywater%20reuse%20at%20home%2C%20explaining%20how%20setting%20up%20a%20filtration%20tank%20for%20just%20Rs%2010%2C000%20can%20conserve%20fresh%20water%20and%20alleviate%20urban%20water%20shortages.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Edible%20Mandap%2C%20Heirloom%20Sarees%3A%20How%20a%20Doctor%20Planned%20Her%20Sustainable%2C%20Farm%20Wedding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20a%20machine%20to%20travel%20back%20in%20time%20at%20Poorvi%20Bhat%20and%20Shamanth%E2%80%99s%20wedding.%20Held%20on%20a%20picturesque%20farm%20in%20Shivamogga%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20event%20felt%20like%20a%20scene%20straight%20out%20of%20a%201960s%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20everything%20a%20wedding%20needed%3A%20two%20people%20in%20love%2C%20happy%20families%2C%20loads%20of%20joy%2C%20scrumptious%20food%2C%20and%20abundant%20happiness.%20What%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20was%20plastic%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291582%2Fplan-green-eco-friendly-indian-wedding-with-ebikes-cycles-in-delhi%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunnecessary%20waste%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20any%20kind%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20food%2C%20plastic%2C%20or%20paper.%20The%20beauty%20of%20the%20union%20was%20enhanced%20by%20the%20simplicity%20of%20the%20setting%2C%20surrounded%20by%20coconut%20trees%2C%20areca%20palms%2C%20mangoes%2C%20and%20lush%20greenery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20everything%20the%20bride%20had%20dreamed%20of%20since%20she%20was%20a%20little%20girl!%20Whenever%20anyone%20asked%20Poorvi%2C%20a%20nutritionist%20and%20naturopath%2C%20what%20she%20wanted%20for%20her%20big%20day%2C%20her%20answer%20remained%20the%20same%20over%20the%20years%3A%20a%20simple%2C%20eco-friendly%20wedding%20at%20her%20family%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20decided%20to%20marry%20her%20husband%2C%20an%20organic%20farmer%2C%20his%20family%20readily%20agreed%20to%20her%20non-negotiable%20requirement%20of%20a%20sustainable%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sugarcane%20mantapa%20doubled%20up%20as%20a%20meal%20for%20the%20cows!%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FCover-image-33-1718768243-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2